[div class=p 
	"The following is an attempt to give Hideo Kojima the editor he should have had.  I see some true potential in Kojima's work, but his game scripts are so artificially bloated by redundancy that I felt the need to step in.  Lines have been cut, sentences have been edited, and sometimes rearranged to create new thoughts altogether.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This is still a work in progress.  I hope you enjoy it.
	$LF
]div
